cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.GR

This paper is about semantic segmentation using convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces new network modules for learning global spatial and channel relationships, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of these modules also involves neural networks (cs.NE) and graph theory (cs.GR).
